-09-24T16:45:32.000Z","msg":"各區聯合個個<br />\n要等每個區搞起咗先得<br />\n<br />\n暫時我諗個個方案係無大台指揮<br />\n而係要當日活動區嘅街坊自發回收物資同供應<br />\n單獨/小隊自發性就可以減少有狗隻放蛇"},{"pid":"a5182a51780e4f64035a6dc487d8bb90c4e8c062","tid":1592600,"uid":164752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:45:34.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16a7c406b5e974f60e521aae5f093f359b3c3515","tid":1592600,"uid":308414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:46:01.000Z","msg":"無論係支持分區集會定係集中遊行 都想你地一齊諗下呢個問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592175</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"33b5000eec61cf41af9d7fc68274740389d58536","tid":1592600,"uid":106870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:47:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"91d8b9e2bdccb9c9671b7903cc12b86858da805a","tid":1592600,"uid":216683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e3149b49a1175d9e57bc33c189efc886e4484b35","tid":1592600,"uid":50598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3cdabd907ec20cb082a6cadb64a3fdad39898460","tid":1592600,"uid":164752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:41:32.000Z","msg":"到時會有大量回收，都會好難收藏"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:44:08.000Z","msg":"只能夠話全民皆兵 化整為零<br />\n由七月提倡到依家 人人都是流動物資站"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:47:19.000Z","msg":"好多都係諗住<br />\n自己準備好自己個套裝<br />\n<br />\n但宜家要變<br />\n就係去到個區就用個區嘅裝<br />\n<br />\n人地去自己個區<br />\n就供人地裝<br />\n<br />\n起馬減少咗<br />\n進場同退場check袋有gear就拉呢個情況"},{"pid":"bf2e094c1a0c855ace608523d0273d5e39e2ec52","tid":1592600,"uid":216683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:48:16.000Z","msg":"暫時只要大家有共識去做<br />\n就已經可以<br />\n唔洗有人去做指揮"},{"pid":"a4b40c19a3544102c0f11b34a16071103120e2a8","tid":1592600,"uid":216683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-